:: TheKind.Session1.P2_FourSwords_U_Empathic
"This card says the record lives in your *rest.* In the quiet moments — when you're falling asleep, or staring out the window during office hours, or sitting with Kuro on the couch."

Ellen's eyes widen slightly at the dog's name. She didn't tell you that.

(She told Scout once, months ago, when he asked about the sticker on her jacket — a silhouette of an Akita with the name underneath. Scout mentioned it to you. You filed it away. That's how The Kind works.)

"He does this thing where he puts his head on my lap when I'm reading and..." She trails off. Smiles a private smile. "Yeah. That's when I hear it most. The four notes. The quiet times."

