# Eight of Cups — Reversed interpretations

:: TheKind.Session1.P3_EightCups_R_Empathic
"Reversed, this card says you've *tried* to stop looking. You know it might be futile. But you can't let go because letting go feels like letting go of *her.*"

Ellen's breath catches.

"And that's the real block — you've tied the search to your love, and now you can't stop one without betraying the other."

She doesn't say anything for a long time. When she speaks, her voice is smaller.

"If I stop looking, who's listening for her? Who remembers the things she loved?"

The Kind is very quiet. Even the rain seems to hold.

